summary: One thing I love about Peter is that he, like every other human on the planet, struggles to do what’s right.  He entertains the...
body: One thing I love about Peter is that he, like every other human on the planet, struggles to do what’s right. He entertains the thought of turning to a life of crime, but ultimately rejects it. He rarely succumbs to selfishness, but when he does, bad things tend to happen.
